OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine start with clear then
OL,6,Fsunny skies across the region. Any
OL,7,Fearly mist soon clearing. Remaining
OL,8,Fsunny into the afternoon and quickly
OL,9,Ffeeling hot or very hot. Slightly
OL,10,Fcooler near some coasts. Winds light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine night with clear skies
OL,13,Facross the region. Chance of mist
OL,14,Fpatches later in the night. Winds
OL,15,Fremaining light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA similar day to Wednesday
OL,18,Fwith plenty of sunshine and turning
OL,19,Fvery hot for most by afternoon. Cooler
OL,20,Fnear coasts and winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
