OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely dry, sunny and hot throughout.
OL,7,FIsolated thundery showers possible
OL,8,Flater Friday and Saturday. Freshening
OL,9,Fnorth-easterly winds developing by
OL,10,FSaturday, strong across Kent by
OL,11,FSunday. Temperatures well above
OL,12,Faverage.
